&lt;Emco Ltd> said the board approved apublic offering of 75.0 mln dlrs principal amount of 7-1/4 pctconvertible subordinated debentures, maturing April 30, 2002,subject to regulatory approvals.    The debentures will be convertible into common shares atany time up to April 30, 1992 at a price of 17.50 dlrs a share,and then up to April 30, 1997 at 18.50 dlrs a share.    Masco Corp &lt;MAS>, holding 44 pct of Emco, has agreed topurchase 33.0 mln dlrs of the debentures. Underwriters areGordon Capital Corp, Midland Doherty Ltd, Merrill Lynch CanadaInc and Levesque Beaubien Inc. Reuter&#3;